data.description: Looking for a spacious home outside city limits with acreage and room for horses and other farm animals? Take a look at this 4 bedroom 2 bath unique property situated on 2 acres. Outside you'll find a barn, lean to shade, tack room, goat pins, corrals, 4 + carports, covered RV parking, (2) 30 AMP hook-ups, (3) 50 AMP hook-ups, & workshop.  There is so much to mention, this is a must see property! Also located on the property is a non-permanent storage shed that the owner has converted to living quarters, however it is not connected to the septic. With an acceptable offer the small non-permanent guest quarters will convey.  Otis Water Meter to convey.  This property will not qualify for FHA or VA, Cash or Conventional financing only.   Call today for your private showing!
